2. cs.IT (Information Theory) is also likely as the paper derives a closed-form lower bound on the outage probability. 
3. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is a possibility as the paper discusses dynamic route selection. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper deals with network parameters and spatial throughput. 
5. cs.PF (Performance) is a possibility as the paper provides an upper bound on the number of successful transmissions.
